<html>
<table width="500" style="font-size: 14px; color: #4a4a4a;">
    <tr>
        <td>
            <p>Dear {{ first_name }},</p>
            <p>There are some shifts over the next two weeks that require more volunteers. Brothers are especially needed as many shifts require an overseer.</p>
            <p>Please take some time to view the below shifts at <a href="http://cartbooking.com">cartbooking.com</a> to see if you can help:</p>
            <ul>
                {% for data in context %}
                    <li>{{ data.display_date }} - {{ data.location_name }}, {{ data.display_time }}</li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ul>
            <p>Thank you for your willing spirit!</p>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</html>
